name: Eat yourself
description:
As you grow up you look into your past and find your thoughts silly, you see yourself from the top now and you're able to see the walls around yourself in the past.
But some people don't need to spend time to get into that level and view. They learn to stop their emotion an thoughts at the moment and see themselves from a higher angle, they check their situation, their future, and then they will be able to analysis. The moment you find yourself doing it, you have  actually done it while you were doing it already. It feels that you keep eating yourself and when you are done, you get eaten by yourself again.
